</div>
<div class="box banner" id="second">
  <div class="stack">
  <h2 class="center">Web3 and Philanthropy</h2>
    <div class="switcher">
      <div class="box stack">
        <h3 class="center">The Big Idea</h3>
        <p class="center">Charitable giving is broken and we are fixing it.
        Pale Blue is a contribution platform that leverages social sharing and
        applies technology to enable transparency, efficiency, and
        accountability not otherwise possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box stack">
        <h3 class="center">Trace Individual Donation</h3>
        <p class="center">Web3 creates a fully transparent chain of giving.
        Allowing donors to trace where their donations are applied.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="box stack">
        <h3 class="center">We Never Share Your Info</h3>
        <p class="center">Have you ever donated to charity and afterwards you
        have been bombarded by spam? Sketchy middlemen agencies take you for
        suckers and on-sell your details. Take the sucker-free approach with
        our secure platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="center box animate-character">Learn More</button>
  </div>
</div>

